    "client_msg_id": "52e99339-07a4-42ce-b30e-68bc6de3fa30",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "I believe this is effectively a type of wavetable synthesis, but with the table derived from sampling the procedural line graph. Lots of systems akin to this built with Max/MSP or Pd, using the built-in line drawing widgets. (I think it might even be one of the tutorials in Max).\n\nStill cool, though.",
